Laboratory slimes are monsters found inside the Dragonkin Laboratory. They have the ability to quickly multiply if they attack a player using melee. If they do manage to attack, a smaller and weaker dark green slime will appear saying Bloop. These smaller slimes have less health, but use much faster melee attacks. The smaller slimes do not provide experience nor drop anything. The adults will spawn a spawnling once every 2 auto attacks capping at a maximum of 4 spawnlings per adult.

In Story mode its health is reduced by 50% and its damage output is reduced by 90%.
